## Alternative approaches (in case you want even less “app”)

1. **Google Sheets** scoreboard (10 minutes, ultra reliable)
2. **Cast a scoring app** from your phone to the TV (fastest, but can be glitchy)
3. If you want ESP32 involvement: build a **button box** later that hits `/action` endpoints (NEXT / UNDO / BUST / +points)

